{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-6", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "慈悲遺願", "storyInfo": "過去與未來，特蕾西婭在源石的資訊之海中瞥見了生命的答案。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$desolate_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一場永遠不會終結的遠行。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾魂的言語早已沉寂，身影也幾乎在長久的磋磨中失去了形狀。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有他們的魔王，仍在替所有人前行。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭不願停下腳步。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去她也曾數度走向“魔王”深處。但這次與以前任何一次漫步都有所不同。她不再為那些浩瀚的知識駐足。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只是在看。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一次，用她自己的眼睛，看向那些大地上的人與事——"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生的，或尚未發生的。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g4_towerroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她最後還是走到了這一步。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#3$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該說我們的殿下什麼好？冥頑不靈，還是天賦異禀？算了，不管罵還是誇，這下連眾魂都聽不見了。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的事情暫時放一邊吧。那邊的爛攤子特雷西斯和孽茨雷會收拾的。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來……哈，瓦瑟領的高塔上塞滿了軍事委員會的間諜。他們恨不得慫恿羊和貓立刻大幹一架，好讓他們別關注卡茲戴爾。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把你們的線都收收好！記住，我們也很快就要滾蛋了。浮誇羊不會容忍我們繼續在她眼皮底下蹦躂。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就跟菈瑪蓮抱怨過，那對兄妹太激進了，遲早會給我們招來數不清的麻煩事！", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃芒加德，你在卡茲戴爾的活兒得加緊做了。 ", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是特雷西斯的計畫沒完全成功，維多利亞……不，萊塔尼亞和其他核心圈國家的軍隊會立刻朝卡茲戴爾行進。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接收巴別塔留下的遺產，保住那座城市。不能讓兩百年前的事再來一次。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等等。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "線頭是不是動了？埃芒加德，是你動的嗎？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣啊。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "弗萊蒙特", "content": "“希望”……我可不怎麼喜歡聽見這個字。但好歹，眼前還算有條路可以走……"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "弗萊蒙特", "content": "對吧，殿下？"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭看到老巫妖嚴肅的臉上露出了一個幾不可見的微笑。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她鬆開了那根透明的、深入虛空的絲弦，朝那位暫停了抱怨的老朋友點了點頭，又朝更遠的地方走去。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g2_glacier", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#1$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#1$3"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#8$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看見，那處影子有了變化。", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#8$3"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是噩兆？", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#10$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#8$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不全是。", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#8$3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來尋我，將遠見的結果告知，我很感激。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我心意已決。邪魔帶來的污染正在蔓延，如果我們一而再再而三地往南退，薩米的淪陷將是遲早的事。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#1$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便，我見到的關於你的所有未來……皆是悲劇？", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#1$3"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早在我成為雪祀……不，在我降生於這片冰原，成長為一名薩米戰士起，我就知曉了自己的結局。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不畏懼死亡。我也不憂慮邪魔奪取我的軀殼，令我轉化為播撒污穢的敵人。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會有更年輕的戰士循著我的足印，走向更北的北方。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若不幸與被轉化的我相遇，他們會用弓和法杖清除我殘軀上的污濁。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然守護薩米的意志不會輕易死去，我便不會視這樣的結果為“悲劇”。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼……祝福你，遠征之人。", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#8$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請拿著這個吧。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "密文板？", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#5$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨別贈禮。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，多數獨眼巨人已做出離開薩米諸部族的決定。而你則選擇了留下來。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一則預言……關於這片土地上的生機，我必須令它實現。", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲，薩米會感謝你這麼多年來的付出。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對我分享了你的遠見，我也贈予你我聽到的聲音。", "name": "埃克提爾尼爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_968_1#8$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角聲響徹冰原。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是遠征的訊號，也是悠遠的致意。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的獨眼巨人或許不會再回到卡茲戴爾，這片冰封之地已然是她的家。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的視線與艾爾啟的視線重疊。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在雪祀留下的木板上看見了奇妙的紋路。"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“埃克綸”。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "草木獸羽有枯榮……"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祈願久延存"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g26_dusk_wild", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……找到了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個讀數……一定就在附近。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step1", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心。我的計算不可能出錯，所以，我們目前就踩在哥倫比亞……不，所有現代國家最偉大的考古發現正上方。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那立刻穿一個洞，將導能電纜和我一起送到下面去，如何？", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#2$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬里亞姆不會高興的。他一定更希望我們小心地探索和發掘。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，誰叫他一直待在北地不回來呢？負責幹這活的是工程科。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在通知你之前，我的人已經開工了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好。", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "介意我當第一個下去的人嗎？", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_originiumcastshort", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）“衛護”。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你很少在工作場合使用咒語。", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先我得確保面前的人不會被這些薩卡茲的小把戲嚇垮。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總轄女士，我本該再念幾句安全須知，但你也不會有心思聽的。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍隊和梅蘭德的人馬上就要找過來了。無論你希望找到什麼——都必須快點了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_891_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會的。", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在死亡的陰翳蒙上我的雙眼之前……我會盡力去看我想見的一切。", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#4$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g8_storage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭看見了。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間又前進了一點。她能感覺到這個地方在拒斥她。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起多年前，自己跟著凱爾希，第一次靠近羅德島本艦的最深處。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個相似的地方，是她從未踏足之地，一片……屬於“神明”的居所。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energybody", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）那個可愛的小傢伙才剛離開……又有新的闖入者。", "name": "“保存者”"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）嗯……沒有嗎？", "name": "“保存者”"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）在你帶來的這些小小的數據漣漪中，我感受到了一絲熟悉。", "name": "“保存者”"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）或許你和我一樣，都是被留在過去，不得已在不屬於自己的時代苟延殘喘的……幽靈。", "name": "“保存者”"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）是什麼支撐著你跋涉至此……一個同樣微弱且渺茫的希望嗎？", "name": "“保存者”"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）還是對無法再見的同類的懷念？", "name": "“保存者”"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g24_cloudy_sea", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spear", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_imp_gunlance_n", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生，小心我的槊，它可能會刮傷您那脆弱的皮膚。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海面之下暫時沒有值得您注意的東西。您在凝望的，究竟是什麼？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一些回憶罷了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經認為阿戈爾遠離大地，面臨的是另一個問題。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但或許……我並不完全正確。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您竟然在這個時候反省。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不希望自己又一次到得太遲。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如海洋的問題並不獨立，那麼我們所面臨的威脅將會疊加在一起。這比任何已知推演中的絕境還要棘手。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，我們有機會在危機被引爆前，先一步抓住主動權。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願等您隨我一同回到阿戈爾，您仍能保持同等程度的自信。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭，我相信的是獵人。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……有趣的說辭。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人從海底來到陸上，又即將回到家鄉。我看著你們一路的變化。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變化……呵呵，這未必是我所期望的。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們會在來處找到自己。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是你，還是斯卡蒂和幽靈鯊，抑或你們那位選擇獨自離去的同伴。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……烏爾比安。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做好準備吧。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，你們會對阿戈爾……對海洋與陸地，對“我們”需要共同面對的浩劫，產生不同的看法。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這遠比任何肉眼可見的“橋樑”有價值。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星星點點的光粒浮起，在海面上投下了清晰的影子。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像凱爾希說的，宛如“橋樑”。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭踏上那座虛空中的橋。時間和浪花一起加速，她很難再掌控自己意識的行進。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希……凱爾希。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭努力地回頭凝望著好友，以及好友身後的新朋友和老朋友——"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到他們和小小的光粒融為一體。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光粒在擴大。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經的魔王發現自己正站在一座教堂中央，沐浴在最聖潔的光下。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而頭頂光環的薩科塔教宗，正與她“對視”著。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於河畔偶遇的年輕信使，教堂窗前的平和老者……她記得他，歲月亦無法干擾她的判斷。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很久沒有新的名字出現了。", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這算不算好事？", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "短短幾年間，我們可多了不少“聖徒”。那裡面的好幾位，我都有些……難以苟同。", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們至今仍未知，聖徒們各自將在未來扮演什麼角色。", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#2$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教宗閣下，既然不再有新的聖徒被選中，是不是意味著……危機有可能已經解除了？", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很樂觀。", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也希望，我們的拉特蘭，能長久地保持這種樂觀。", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而……", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去，它從未緘口不言。", "name": "伊萬杰利斯塔十一世"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_356_1#8$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——！", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，有一瞬間，我感覺不到——", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這怎麼可能？！", "name": "教宗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光熄滅了。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先是一盞燈，然後是一片街區。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從啟示石塔到米迦萊昂區的公證所，再到聖瑪律索區的夕輝禮拜堂，教堂廣場——"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$reawakeningpiano_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑暗在前進。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迅速，無序，不可抵擋。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰原，海洋，陸地。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的訊號都預示著未來人們將遭遇的磨難，就和她無數次透過“魔王”看到的一樣。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g12_sandstorm", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandwnd", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她走出黑暗時，腳下卻已是鬆軟的黃沙。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廢墟，晶簇，沙丘……眼前的一切她如此陌生。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在揚起沙塵的狂風中，她聽到了，看到了，感受到了那位孤獨的少女。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個迎面走來，籠罩在斗篷中的身影，撩起帽簷。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石在少女的腳下如雪痕般綻放，特蕾西婭看到了少女眼中的菱形瞳孔——"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黃沙漫過，她的雙眼已被遮蔽。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wind", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_5_7_shining", "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並非終點，但已是特蕾西婭能夠觸及的最遠處。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑暗正朝她擠壓過來，即將封鎖她的去路，摀住她的眼睛、她的思想。"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有她熱烈的情感，仍在這片永恆的幽暗中蕩漾。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她曾帶著千萬個問題一路跋涉，走到自我的盡頭，卻只渴求著一個最簡單的回答。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i34", "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_tlxy_laugh", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 5.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "“在這些未來，以及更遙遠的未來之中……", "x": 300.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 28.0, "delay": 0.0, "duration": 2.5, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "“還有我愛的人們的影子嗎？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 380.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 28.0, "delay": 0.0, "duration": 2.5, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭迫切地尋找著，看向那黑暗之中唯一的光明處——"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她得到了答案。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 6.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}